betterquesting:10.desc:8:
This place, this strange asteroid belt, this is where the Arbiter came up with Fluix, his gift to the Testificates of Terra.
Things are starting to make sense now, and I think I am starting to see the role I am supposed to play in this story.
How did I not see it before? 
The Arbiter is the master of Fluix; I have been the first person since their fall that has built anything using fluix. 
The Arbiter was a builder. I have built a large industrial base.
The arbiter was there to protect the Testificates, and was ready to die for them...
